latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Apps: Lightroom , Snapseed
Cam: Iphone 12
Shot on Portrait Mode

I do not like adding too much of contrast and Structure too.

👉🏻Please know that everybody’s editing skills is per their choice and it differs. 

Ps : A good cam and a skill to find the right angle and spot is quite essential too.😇

latestIgtvVideos.title: SoapGram😍
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey guys, here is a small tutorial on how to make homemade soaps. 
This is called melt and pour soap creation. 
You can make soaps of your choice with any soap base and ingredients. 
I have mentioned a list of things required to make one and these are available on Amazon.
Enjoy.
(Posting this coz I got a lot of questions on how to make one)

Things Required
✨Soap Base (Here I am using Goat milk base soap)
✨Colorant
✨Fragrance (Here I used the Honey and vanilla mist from Forrest Essentials)
✨Rubbing Alcohol
✨Silicon Mould
✨Honey(Optional)
✨Orange Zest(Optional)
✨Bubble wrap for the Honey comb effecf(optional)
✨Pyrex Beaker
